data.label: 抖音 SDK
data.description: 抖音开放平台 SDK 目前提供了抖音登录 & 授权以及分享至抖音的基本能力。您可以通过接入抖音开放平台 SDK 来使用抖音授权登录您的应用或者分享图片或视频到抖音。

data.label: Douyin SDK
data.description: Douyin Open Platform SDK currently provides basic capabilities for Douyin login & authorization and sharing to Douyin. You can use the Douyin Open Platform SDK to log in to your application with Douyin authorization or share images or videos to Douyin.
